These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, writing
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, tulip
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, november
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | writing       | traveling |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| Flower       | tulip    | azalea    |
| Birthday   | november       | july      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, fishing
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, pall-mall
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | almond-milk |
| Hobby           | baking | fishing      |
| Cigar   | pall-mall  | aristoff      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, librarian
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, country
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, amber
1. the fan of country is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who likes amber##1
3. the fisherman is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk  |
| Job          | fisherman    | librarian   |
| Music-Genre   | country  | ambient   |
| Color     | amber     | white |

