The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, aconite
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, security-guard
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, techno
1. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
2. the nurse is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
3. the old-henry-smoker is the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
