.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-5::.
2 different games are played: poker, scrabble
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, begonia
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, skateboarding
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, roller
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Game         | poker | scrabble   |
| Flower   | bellflower | begonia       |
| Sport         | sailing   | skateboarding |
| Transport     | roller    | quad-bike     |

