2 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg
1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who likes azure is the entrepreneur##1
3. the person who likes brown is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |      2       |
| Hobby         | reading            | board-games  |
| Job           | software-developer | entrepreneur |
| Color   | brown           | azure       |
| Game     | canasta            | mah-jongg        |

