.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
2 different games are played: backgammon, poker
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, superhero
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, chess
1. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Game           | poker | backgammon     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime          | superhero |
| Pet           | mouse          | rabbit    |
| Hobby     | chess            | card-games       |

 